{"tid":1762110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人民日報：港人慶祝《人權法》簽署成法 , 奴相十足、醜態百出","createTime":"2019-11-29T10:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T14:00:53.000Z","uid":25468,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b138addaaa2788f6600375068a709d69742896","tid":1762110,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"人民日報發表評論文章，批評美國將《香港人權與民主法案》簽署成法，指中國並不缺乏反制工具。<br />\n<br />\n文章指美方用國內法處理國際事務，是對中國內政的粗暴干涉，嚴重損害香港同胞共同利益，但香港將這種赤裸裸的霸權行徑，當作最好的感恩節禮物，並舉行活動慶祝，是奴相十足、醜態百出，強調美國絕不是香港的恩主，又指香港的繁榮穩定，受到「一國兩制」的制度保障，不會輕易因某一國家推出的某一法例而動搖，中國並不缺少見招拆招的反制工具，更不缺少維護香港繁榮穩定的決心和能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/12143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F12143&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=96e1320c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F12143&h=2774716f\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/12143</a>"},{"pid":"e6264682a1a019f6c9b111a66a4fc1a88192daab","tid":1762110,"uid":231234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"竟然冇強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75abb642d1a06d452f661e2118c1cf4455de4dc2","tid":1762110,"uid":15605,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjPaff4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjPaff4.jpg&h=9d9c6f3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2d1d52a0c918bbe2ffb4e0e26c0b40433472a2","tid":1762110,"uid":4942,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"//中國並不缺少見招拆招的反制工具//<br />\n<br />\n例如呢？ 點解唔講黎聽下？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa19c6f981c672723d952e9955342b749dfdda56","tid":1762110,"uid":6347,"like":4,"dis